HEADWORD: Fifty
<hw>Fif"ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>f⟦imac⟧ftig</ets>; akin to OHG. <ets>finfzug</ets>,
<ets>fimfzuc</ets>, G. <ets>f⟦uum⟧nfzig</ets>, <ets>funfzig</ets>, Goth.
<ets>fimftigjus</ets>. See <er>Five</er>, and <er>Ten</er>, and cf.
<er>Fifteen</er>.]</ety> <def>Five times ten; <as>as, <ex>fifty</ex>
men</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
