==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Fifty
<hw>Fif"ty</hw>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Fifties</plw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The sum of five tens; fifty units
or objects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A symbol representing fifty units, as 50, or
l.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

